flowchart LR
  ENG[Engineers / Approvers] --> PORTAL[Portal and API]
  SOURCES[VMware / Xen / Kubernetes / Monitoring / Logs / ITSM / Automation] --> OBS[Observer and Connector Runtime]
  OBS --> STREAM[Canonical Event Stream]
  STREAM --> DATA[Telemetry and Metadata Stores]
  DATA --> GRAPH[Knowledge and Decision Graph]
  DATA --> EVID[Evidence Engine]
  GRAPH --> EVID
  EVID --> REASON[Reasoner / Predictor / Guardian / Advisor]
  REASON --> POLICY[Policy and Approval]
  POLICY --> ORCH[Orchestrator]
  ORCH --> TOOLS[AWX / Terraform / PowerCLI / GitLab]
  REASON --> EVAL[AI Evaluation and Governance]
  ORCH --> EVAL
  EVAL --> PORTAL
